reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent laptop for the price. Easy to use, and setup. Great quality.
reviews.reviewText: So far no issues with this laptop. Not only is the color great, but it runs smoothly and no problems thus far.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Screen resolution clearer than my future TBH
reviews.reviewText: I already read the other reviews so I knew the speakers were not very powerful, but I just needed a lightweight laptop with light up keys to work quietly at night while kids sleep. The speakers are a bit tinny and quiet, but the laptop works excellently with Bluetooth headphones (or AUX). It comes with a bonus mouse, mousepad, and a cute little kawaii magnet bookmark which was a nice touch. The charger looks nonstandard for what I’m used to (very short cord), but make sure you’re plugging into the small round port on the left side of the laptop, not the AUX port on the right side. There will be a small indicator light if you plugged it into the power port properly! The laptop is lightweight, and the screen is super big for the size of the laptop because it has very little in the way or frame or bevel. I powered it up with no issues, and Windows is already all set. Ran a few updates and tried out a YT video on highest resolution (Halazia by Ateez) and was blown away by the resolution and screen image quality. It’s beautiful really. I’m gonna switch to using this laptop to stream video (with headphones) because the video quality is so clear and crisp and bright. The purple outer is all smooth, comes wrapped in clingy protective film (which I’ll leave on until my BTS stickers arrive), and it’s pretty light. I would not treat this item as if it were a rugged built chassis IMO—it’s very lightweight plastic (I already bought a protective case…color matches to F¡ntie purple or lavender laptop case). That’s all I’ve got for now, but I’ll update if anything changes my opinion of this device as I continue to use it! Thx for reading if you got this far.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice laptop computer
reviews.reviewText: This laptop performs fine for the functions that my daughter uses it for - general schoolwork - e-mail, word, excel and general internet surfacing - which was why I was happy it came with MSOffice and NOT the 365 version. She is not a gamer, so she doesn't need to track satellite positioning. And with Barbie being the hot item right now - the color was perfect. It's very light-weight and came well protected in the shipping box and comes with a pink mouse - another Barbie Bonus. It was hard to track down, but the warranty is the very common 1-year duration. On a sidenote, the Barbie stickers that were on her stocking went immediately on the laptop shell.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars One problem after another
reviews.reviewText: Love the color and big screen. However, the power cord they sent broke within the first month, being so short that I pulled it out of the port 3 times by accident. When I tried to determine what kind of cord to purchase, I could not find on specs anywhere. No computer store I called had EVER heard of this brand, so I ordered six cords before I found the right size.It froze once and I had to let it run out of power before I could get it to reset. I asked for my money back that time but dealing with assurance is a nightmare. I spent over 2 hours trying to file a claim before I was hung up on, thereby negating all that work.The touch pad is not working again. The first time it happened, I have no idea why it started again. This time it has been 3 days since it works and I have had to purchase a mouse so I can use my laptop.Do not buy this! You get what you pay for and this isn't worth it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I needed a laptop for school and the main thing that caught my eye was the color. I love purple and when it came in yesterday, let me tell you it is absolutely amazing. Everything is simple not to mention it came with a keyboard protector and a cordless mouse with a comfortable grip. It also lights up which is a nice bonus and has the right amount of space needed for my schoolwork. I'm excited to play with around with it more.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars So pretty and such a great deal!
reviews.reviewText: This was an amazing deal for this laptop. I love the color and it runs fast and smooth. Some people were complaining that you can't see the keyboard too much, which is partially true but they did include this black silicone to put over the keyboard and I actually enjoy using it. They included a cute mouse which was really nice. I love the fast log in with finger print scanner. I just needed a laptop to work on for my CPA studying so I didn't want anything super fancy and this was just perfect. Love the price point and love the look. Would recommend.
